{
  "name": "Greater Chakra Pill",
  "type": "consumable",
  "img": "icons/commodities/gems/pearl-swirl-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid13\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">An edible pill that contains a drug designed to super </span><span dir=\"ltr\">charge the person who consumes it, bodies, stamina </span><span dir=\"ltr\">recovery.</span> </span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid13\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">Consuming a chakra pill takes a bonus action. </span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid13\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">A Creature who takes this pill regains Chakra points </span><span dir=\"ltr\">equal to the quality of the pill consumed.</span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid14\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">A creature can only regain chakra artificially in this </span><span dir=\"ltr\">way a limited number of times.<br />You can regain chakra </span><span dir=\"ltr\">using this consumable 5 times per long rest. </span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid14\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">If you</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">would </span><span dir=\"ltr\">attempt to consume this pill any additional time after </span><span dir=\"ltr\">this use limit, you spend 1 chakra die, and regain 1d4+1.</span></span></p>",
